channel.title: RSC Private server client - how to deobfuscate?
channel.description:
Hi, I tried to decompile a client for a private server. DJ Java Decompiler or JAD didn't make it, guess it's obfuscated. As it's a private server I didn't spend time looking for RSC deobfuscators as they might be using something completely different.
Here is the client I need to be deobfuscated: [url=http://www.speedyshare.com/252189899.html]http://www.speedyshare.com/252189899.html[/url]
Would be thankful for any tips or help, but the best would be is someone deobed it for me.
Thanks.
